t`コントロールの`value`を整数型に変換して他の変数（例：`num`）に格納","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8181-9b38-f9d94c972d6a","type":"numbered_list_item","parent":"2. `num`を一つ増やす","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81c9-ac86-c7fb47c7c6d8","type":"numbered_list_item","parent":"3. `num`を文字列型に変換して、`ft.Text`コントロールの`value`に格納","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81a9-9aff-c4ceac8bb332","type":"numbered_list_item","parent":"4. `ft.Text`コントロールを`update`する","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-810d-b7c0-dd531e7b9858","parent":"※ファイルは「flet-prac3.py」として保存","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8123-9c59-c3c31e4a10c9","type":"heading_1","parent":"# 進捗アンケート","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81aa-aec8-dafb6a31221e","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81a6-83e4-f87d39d43b71","parent":"この問題が終了した人は、以下のGoogleフォームに回答してください。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8110-b2d6-f9f4ce7c5ad9","parent":"回答後、練習問題の回答例のURLをメールでお送りします。","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8163-a603-fbef7ad47608","type":"quote","parent":"> ","children":[{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81e1-8616-f079aa45f2cf","type":"bookmark","parent":"[bookmark](https://forms.gle/FFBeAXNS5VA5AJV29)","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81b9-a4c8-c72951bd4602","type":"paragraph","parent":"","children":[]}]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"前期","id":"/posts/course/前期"},{"title":"Flet","id":"/posts/curriculums/17d2297f-7a72-8043-ada8-c111deeeb4d7/17d2297f-7a72-8043-ada8-c111deeeb4d7"},{"id":"/posts/curriculums/17d2297f-7a72-8043-ada8-c111deeeb4d7/17d2297f-7a72-80f3-b72b-d2e514002c10","title":"Fletの練習問題3"}],"childrenData":{"title":"Flet","childPages":[{"title":"0. GUIとFletについて","id":"17d2297f-7a72-8052-85a5-e7de3049579f"},{"title":"1. Fletのインストール","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80a2-b044-e17924cfa345"},{"title":"2. カウンターを作ってみよう","id":"17d2297f-7a72-803c-829b-ea2844416